@gillianoberholzer @shaunviljoen @jakovanrensburg 
Hi - we won't be able to serve this search to client.
The XML returned from DeedsOffice has a fault in it.
Here is an excerpt of the Raw XML:
  <INTO-TR/VB>2015/05/13 11:07:46</INTO-TR/VB>
  <OUT-OF-TR/VB>2015/05/18 13:45:40</OUT-OF-TR/VB>
  <INTO-MICRO>2015/05/19 07:46:18</INTO-MICRO>


There cannot be a "/" in the tag, (INTO-TR/VB).
it will break when you try to use it.
